{"id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0000", "text": "[Knowledge article](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/actueel.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0000", "source_slug": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel", "source_title": "How teenagers use ransomware as a revenue model", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel.html", "source_date": "2025-07-21", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 0, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 0}}
{"id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0001", "text": "[Cyber attack](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberattack/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0001", "source_slug": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel", "source_title": "How teenagers use ransomware as a revenue model", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel.html", "source_date": "2025-07-21", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 1, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 1}}
{"id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0002", "text": "The world of cybercrime is changing rapidly. We first thought about adult hackers in dark rooms. Nowadays, young teenagers, sometimes not yet eighteen years old, use ransomware to extort money from companies. For them, hacking is not a game – they see it as a business.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0002", "source_slug": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel", "source_title": "How teenagers use ransomware as a revenue model", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel.html", "source_date": "2025-07-21", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 2}}
{"id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0003", "text": "[Ransomware](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/wat-is-ransomware.html) is malicious software that young cyber criminals use to make money. Young people with technical aptitude can find simple tools and manuals online, with which they can quickly carry out attacks. Some of them earn thousands of euros per month. They target small businesses without proper security and demand ransoms in cryptocurrency. They often remain beyond the reach of investigative services.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0003", "source_slug": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel", "source_title": "How teenagers use ransomware as a revenue model", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel.html", "source_date": "2025-07-21", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 3}}
{"id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "What starts as a curious exploration of digital systems, in some cases results in organized extortion. Young people read other people's success stories on forums, Discord groups or Telegram chats and get seduced. Before they know it, they are participating in a network that spreads ransomware, targets and distributes revenue.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel", "source_title": "How teenagers use ransomware as a revenue model", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel.html", "source_date": "2025-07-21", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
{"id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "There are several reasons why young people are so susceptible to this criminal path:", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel", "source_title": "How teenagers use ransomware as a revenue model", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel.html", "source_date": "2025-07-21", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "- Financial temptation: The prospect of making a lot of money quickly is irresistible, especially for young people with no income.\n- Easy access: Software and explanations are available free or cheaply. Tools are offered ready to use.\n- Anonymity and underestimation: Many young perpetrators think they are elusive. They do not realize that IP addresses, payment trails and chat logs can be traced.\n- Lack of guidance: Young people with a talent for IT do not always receive the right guidance or examples of ethical use of their skills.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel", "source_title": "How teenagers use ransomware as a revenue model", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel.html", "source_date": "2025-07-21", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "The financial return seems attractive, but the consequences are severe. Young people who are caught not only have to deal with criminal law, but put their entire future at risk:", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel", "source_title": "How teenagers use ransomware as a revenue model", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel.html", "source_date": "2025-07-21", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "- No Certificate of Good Conduct (VOG).\n- Exclusion from certain studies or internships.\n- Problems with international travel or visa applications.\n- Reputational damage in a digital world that forgets nothing.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel", "source_title": "How teenagers use ransomware as a revenue model", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel.html", "source_date": "2025-07-21", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig](https://www.samendigitaalveilig.nl/).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel", "source_title": "How teenagers use ransomware as a revenue model", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel.html", "source_date": "2025-07-21", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
{"id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0010", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0010", "source_slug": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel", "source_title": "How teenagers use ransomware as a revenue model", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel.html", "source_date": "2025-07-21", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 10}}
{"id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0011", "text": "- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) and reduce your cyber risks.\n- View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars on our [Safe entrepreneurship page](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link).\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel__a2-late-chunking__0011", "source_slug": "hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel", "source_title": "How teenagers use ransomware as a revenue model", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/hoe-tieners-ransomware-inzetten-als-verdienmodel.html", "source_date": "2025-07-21", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 11, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 11}}
